node.text:
At CASETiFY, we care for you and our planet. 🌏 To show our love and support for #TheresNoPlanetB, we have brought 6 artists together to use their creativity to make a difference by showing positive changes to our environment. 🌱 ⁠
⁠
Our new “No Planet B” Collection  ranges from floral to nature prints on our ultra compostable cases which is 100% compostable, made with plant based material and printed with eco-friendly soy ink. ♻️ Let's join forces to make our world a better place. #DropToZero⁠

node.text: “you get what you give” what does this quote mean to you? at CASETiFY we acknowledge that you reap what we sow. while no one is perfect, make a conscious effort to be kind to others and treat them the way you want to be treated, so they will return the behaviour. design by @quotesbychristie⁠⁠

together we are one ☝️ Coke x CASETiFY is LIVE! celebrate the 50th anniversary of the @cocacola Hilltop advertisement with protective tech accessories covered with electric designs inspired by the iconic advertisement. 🕺  bring back those 70's vibes and celebrate peace, hope, unity & optimism with us!

you heard of the new 𝒹𝓇𝑒𝒶𝓂 𝓉𝑒𝒶𝓂 (aka #SpaceJamxCASETiFY collaboration)? 🙌  our new dreamy galactic glitter case features the whole @spacejammovie 𝕥𝕦𝕟𝕖 𝕤𝕢𝕦𝕒𝕕 with 6.6ft drop protection (think: 3.5 basketball hoops high!). basically, it's a slam dunk! be the first to know the launch at link in bio.⁠

#SpaceJamxCASETiFY is launching on Aug 31st.⁠
#spacejammovie
